ZH: 我今天戴着一个漂亮的项链去参加派对。
EN: I wore a beautiful necklace to the party today.

ZH: 她收到了一条非常贵重的项链作为生日礼物。
EN: She received a very precious necklace as a birthday present.

ZH: 这件项链上的宝石非常闪亮。
EN: The gemstones on this necklace are very shiny.

ZH: 她的项链是由纯银制成的。
EN: Her necklace is made of pure silver.

ZH: 我买了一条具有特殊意义的项链，送给了我的母亲。
EN: I bought a necklace with special meaning and gave it to my mother.

ZH: 她正在修理那条项链，因为它的链子断了。
EN: She is repairing the necklace because the chain is broken.

ZH: 我的项链突然在路上丢失了，我很难过。
EN: I lost my necklace suddenly on the way, I am very sad.

ZH: 这条项链上挂着一个小心形吊坠。
EN: There is a small heart-shaped pendant hanging on this necklace.

ZH: 你可以选择一个合适的项链来搭配你的服装。
EN: You can choose a suitable necklace to match your outfit.

ZH: 她一直佩戴着一条幸运项链，它给她带来好运。
EN: She always wears a lucky necklace that brings her good luck.

ZH: 那个女孩正在选择一个漂亮的项链来与她的礼服相配。
EN: The girl is choosing a beautiful necklace to match her evening gown.

ZH: 这条项链的设计非常独特，吸引了很多人的目光。
EN: The design of this necklace is very unique and has attracted a lot of attention.

ZH: 我把项链放在了我的首饰盒里，以保持它的美丽。
EN: I put the necklace in my jewelry box to keep its beauty.

ZH: 我的姐姐得到了一枚金质项链作为奖励。
EN: My sister received a gold necklace as a reward.

ZH: 项链上挂着一颗闪耀的蓝宝石，非常引人注目。
EN: There is a sparkling blue sapphire hanging on the necklace, very eye-catching.

ZH: 这条项链是她用海洋贝壳手工制作而成的。
EN: This necklace is handcrafted by her using seashells.

ZH: 我在海边拾取了一块琥珀，并将其加工成了一条项链。
EN: I picked up a piece of amber on the beach and made it into a necklace.

ZH: 这条珍珠项链给她增添了优雅和魅力。
EN: This pearl necklace adds grace and charm to her.

ZH: 他戴着一条项链，上面镶嵌着许多彩色的宝石。
EN: He is wearing a necklace with many colorful gemstones set in it.

ZH: 她把项链挂在了镜子上，以便随时可以看到它。
EN: She hung the necklace on the mirror so that she can see it anytime.
